sequenceDiagram
    participant Host as Host Client
    participant P as Participant Client
    participant Sync as sync-service

    Host->>Sync: SEND {"type": "PLAY", "payload": {"timestamp": 12345}}
    Sync->>Sync: Validate sender is the room's host
    alt Sender is Host
        Sync->>Sync: Update authoritative room state (isPlaying: true)